name: Inuki
description: The Lucky Shiba from East China is a meme token born with serenity and style deployed with love on @BONKDOTFUN. This small-eyed, big-bagged Shiba doesn’t chase charts it meditates before mooning. Fusing Eastern meme aesthetics with Solana degen culture, it’s calm, chaotic, and full of charm. With community-driven energy, unique branding, and playful minimalism, Lucky Shiba stands out as a symbol of silent strength and surprising fortune. The moon is inevitable but only after meditation.
